# IntelliSearch AI - Appian Knowledge Retrieval System

A professional, enterprise-grade AI solution for intelligent knowledge retrieval in Appian Case Management systems.

## Features

- **AI-Powered Semantic Search**: Natural language understanding for policy documents
- **Real-time Integration**: Seamless integration with Appian Case Management
- **Smart Document Processing**: Automatic classification and tagging
- **Advanced Analytics**: Real-time insights and performance metrics
- **Secure Authentication**: JWT-based authentication with role-based access
- **Responsive Design**: Modern, professional UI across all devices

## Technology Stack

### Frontend
- HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)
- Chart.js for data visualization
- Responsive design with CSS Grid/Flexbox
- Font Awesome icons

### Backend
- Python Flask
- SQLAlchemy ORM
- JWT Authentication
- RESTful API architecture

### Database
- SQLite (development)
- PostgreSQL ready (production)

## Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/intellisearch-ai.git
cd intellisearch-ai